      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779212598906,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Unit of User Interface\n\n- Responsible for a portion of \"screen real estate\"\n    - Can be materialized by using a selector or through a route. \n    - Pages - they \"show up\" by going to a route. The selector isn't used.\n\n    - Accurately project the application state to the user \n        - almost *always* so that they can make decisions on what actions to take\n          based on that data.\n        - \"actions\" - affordances through which the user can change the state,\n           express intent, etc.\n\n        - the data that is projected on the component can change\n          underneath the component and get out of date.\n\n\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Unit of User Interface\n\n- Responsible for a portion of \"screen real estate\"\n    - Can be materialized by using a selector or through a route. \n    - Pages - they \"show up\" by going to a route. The selector isn't used.\n\n    - Accurately project the application state to the user \n        - almost *always* so that they can make decisions on what actions to take\n          based on that data.\n        - \"actions\" - affordances through which the user can change the state,\n           express intent, etc.\n\n        - the data that is projected on the component can change\n          underneath the component and get out of date.\n\n\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
