      "text": "Typescript -> (compiled 'transpiled') -> JavaScript\nTemplates (.html) -> ivy -> JavaScript\n\n\nGET / (user gets the application)\n\nindex.html -  ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Typescript -> (compiled 'transpiled') -> JavaScript\nTemplates (.html) -> ivy -> JavaScript\n\n\nGET / (user gets the application)\n\nindex.html -  ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "HbIYAdByBhNs4_aLiyE7X",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 448,
      "y": 2512,
      "width": 1001,
      "height": 200,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aD",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 302130323,
      "version": 466,
      "versionNonce": 1511724307,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779216090920,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "Many small JavaScript files are WAY better than one big one.\n- Two reasons:\n    - The browser has to run all of main.js before *anything* shows up on the screen.\n    - ANY changes in your angular app (this app) will create a new version.\n    - EVERYTIME a user requests, they have to download main.js.\n - the \"features\" (areas)\n    - changes in these should only require THAT feature and main.js to be downloaded again.\n    ",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "Many small JavaScript files are WAY better than one big one.\n- Two reasons:\n    - The browser has to run all of main.js before *anything* shows up on the screen.\n    - ANY changes in your angular app (this app) will create a new version.\n    - EVERYTIME a user requests, they have to download main.js.\n - the \"features\" (areas)\n    - changes in these should only require THAT feature and main.js to be downloaded again.\n    ",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "PfcxdMlF1p0veWF6VX5Bv",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 454,
      "y": 2799,
      "width": 1111,
      "height": 125,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "aE",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 2027582355,
      "version": 325,
      "versionNonce": 1539948893,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1779216727552,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "index.html - should be set to \"no-cache\"\n    - it's TINY - like a tcp frame. Nothing in it. You want it fresh.\n    - everything else (all javascript, all css, etc.) should be cached as immutable, forever (1 year)\n    - every time I look at your templates here at, they are wrong on this. they won't listen to me.\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 8,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "index.html - should be set to \"no-cache\"\n    - it's TINY - like a tcp frame. Nothing in it. You want it fresh.\n    - everything else (all javascript, all css, etc.) should be cached as immutable, forever (1 year)\n    - every time I look at your templates here at, they are wrong on this. they won't listen to me.\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    }
